            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">A couple of months back we featured Luis Serrano‚Äôs excellent book on Grokking Machine Learning. <a href="https://content.alegion.com/podcast/grokking-machine-learning-with-luis-serrano" target="_self">Listen</a> to Luis discuss a bit more about his book and his journey to becoming a successful educator in the field of ML.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
